SUMMARY:An Introduction to Watercolor Painting 
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nThis class offers an introduction to the essential techniques 
 of the medium\, including transparent layering through glazing\, color 
 mixing\, brush control\, and composition. Discover how watercolor moves 
 effortlessly between control and spontaneity—where precision intermingles 
 with the beauty of “happy accidents.” Class is for both beginners and 
 students with previous experience.\n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Tower Room\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
