SUMMARY:Italian Conversation - Online
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to register on 
 the Adult School website.\n\nThis class is appropriate for those who have 
 some basic knowledge of Italian\, Each class focuses on the use of Italian 
 and cultural knowledge for communicating in a variety of situations 
 including shopping\, sightseeing\, making reservations\, dining out and 
 having a simple conversation with others.  Students will speak using the 
 present tense and will be introduced to simple grammar to express past 
 time.  We will review many relevant expressions and vocabulary in context. 
 This course will be appropriate for students who have completed Italian for 
 Travelers 1 and 2 or Basic Italian 1 & 2.\n
LOCATION:Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Language
