SUMMARY:Let's Listen To...Alto Sax: Beyond B-Bop (MPL Auditorium)
DESCRIPTION:Curator and renowned saxophonist/composer/educator Rudresh 
 Mahanthappa guides us through the music of alto players who innovated and 
 set the pace in the wake of Charlie Parker\, Jackie McLean\, Eric Dolphy\, 
 Steve Coleman\, and Gary Bartz\, to name a few. A longtime Montclair 
 resident\, Rupresh is one of the leading voices pushing jazz forward. He 
 has won best altoist in the famed DownBeat Critics Poll an astounding nine 
 times. His records consistently receive critical praise. Since 2019\, 
 Rupresh has been director of jazz at Princeton University.
