SUMMARY:Live Free St. Patrick's Irish Harp and Flute Concert
DESCRIPTION:This is a free Adult School event. Click here to register on 
 the Adult School website.\n\nCome celebrate with the gift of live Irish 
 music! Linda Hickman and Iris Nevins of the Folklife Center of Northern New 
 Jersey will delight you with traditional Irish flute and harp music\, from 
 ancient Celtic tunes to dance music\, and share some of the history behind 
 the heritage. The Folklife Center of Northern New Jersey is a co-sponsored 
 project of the New Jersey State Council on the Arts\, with additional 
 support from the National Endowment for the Arts and Passaic County 
 Community College.
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Auditorium\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
