SUMMARY:LIVING GREEN: Gardening for the Birds NEW
DESCRIPTION:This is a free Adult School event. Registration is required. 
 Click here to register on the Adult School website.\n\nWould you like to 
 entice beautiful birds to your backyard?  Is there anything better than a 
 hummingbird visiting your block party? Sadly\, American songbirds are 
 rapidly diminishing in numbers. You will learn how to support them by 
 creating an attractive habitat for birds with native flowers and bushes 
 from Deb Ellis\, Master Gardener and leader of the Essex Chapter of the 
 Native Plants Society. A question and answer period will follow.
