SUMMARY:Tech Help Tuesdays: One-on-One Tech Help
DESCRIPTION:Drop in during this weekly open session for technology related 
 help on using your cellphone\, tablet\, or computer.\n\n\nWant to feel more 
 confident using technology? Join us for Tech Help Tuesdays—a casual\, 
 drop-in space where adults can receive one-on-one assistance with everyday 
 tech challenges.\n\nRegistration is required as only one staff member is 
 available to assist at this time. 20 minutes are allotted per 
 patron.\n\nPlease note that some technological issues may be above the 
 ability of the library staff and you may be referred out to a better suited 
 tech professional. These drop-ins are not professional IT services\, we 
 cannot fix computers or smartphones.
