SUMMARY:Mindfulness Meditation
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nMindfulness is meditation practice that cultivates positive 
 states of mind like gratitude\, kindness and compassion. We will cover 
 techniques for feeling more connected to our bodies and emotional states. 
 We will also provide support for developing a daily sitting practice. This 
 meditation technique can be quite helpful with reduction of stress and 
 emotion regulation. We will cover the following topics: mindful 
 breathing/body\,\n
