SUMMARY:Mah Jongg Meetup -  Weekly Thursday Morning
DESCRIPTION:PLEASE NOTE: You must sign up for EACH INDIVIDUAL SESSION. 
 Signing up for one session does not register you for any following 
 classes.\n\nThe Mah Jongg Meetup provides a weekly opportunity for players 
 to continue practicing their established skills\, sharpen their 
 strategies\, build confidence at the game table\, and socialize with fellow 
 Mah Jongg players!\n\nThe library will provide a set and table! NOTE: 
 Attendees should already have an understanding of the Mah Jongg game. 
 Attendees should bring their 2025 or 2026 National Mah Jongg League card to 
 the meetup. Bringing an additional set is encouraged!\n\nIf you're new to 
 the game\, and would like to teach yourself at your own pace\, please 
 register for the "Mah Jongg Self-Paced Learning Space" by clicking here.\n
